channel.title: The Best Server In The World? [pictures] Sigex - SoulScape v6.0
channel.description:
[center]Right I'm not sure were i would but so here seems good pfft![/center] [center]A few pictures of a soon to be public server.[/center]
[First a bit about me and the history of SoulScape]
I started of as you average annoying noob, asking all the questions no one ever wanted to answer after some time adding shops, and other noob stuff like that. I soon started working out how other things worked like commands and using items on item and other basic packets like those. Once I hade sucked the life and “code to large my server” I removed it all and started on other stuff after a long time of being a stupid gay on my computer and hours and hours of not stop coding and reading I started to make bigger and better things by looking at how other people hade made there stuff I was able to make similar scripts. This helped me a lot and I now read and find data in my server a lot easier and know were every thing was gave me a big boast! And I was away I have made 6 version of SoulScape and the bases I used I tough there was nothing better..
TestScape v1 PimpScape v2 Project 16 v3 Project 16 blitz v4 Project 16 blitz v5.0 – 5.4
And now Dodian after spending some time reading all the content I felt that this was the best choice I hade. And wow I was wrong.. but after I hade cleaned up the bugs it was the perfect base to make the game we so hate and love “RuneScape” my account hade been banned from RuneScape and this has made me hate RuneScape so I am now remaking the game we use* to enjoy (before jagex killed RuneScape)
I would like to say all code I make I make my self. I am now working on SoulScape v6.0 and its coming along nicer each day I fill I get smarter better ways of making what I do and don’t have better.
[center] I have added a few video links to youtube videos of the server, please keep in mind that the videos show copyright content and will soon beremoved (not of my choice...) [/center]

item.description:
@Java_Is_My_Bitch wrote:

What’s the song in the pking video?

Oh and a suggestion stop writing in blue its so damn annoying, l2Spell correctly, keyword, hint hint.

For animations, you could always make a loop to run like through 20K animations at a time interval, but your client is gonna crash, you can just make 1000000 commands with different animation numbers.

Oh and:

snowycards:

sigex can you teach me how to enhance stats? like 15% more strength

Called 5th Grade math, multiply the stat level by the percentage, move the decimal two times to the right making it a decimal.

So 15% would be .15

99Strength * .15 = 14.85 + 99 = New Strength Level.
